spectacularly.

00:37:39.690 --> 00:37:43.070
So I think the biggest threat
to "Sharknado's" continued

00:37:43.070 --> 00:37:49.200
success is them trying
to manufacture it.

00:37:49.200 --> 00:37:53.080
And that's a concern,
because we're

00:37:53.080 --> 00:37:55.360
trying to walk a
tight rope, I guess,

00:37:55.360 --> 00:37:57.400
between getting the
word out and not

00:37:57.400 --> 00:38:02.060
making it seem like this is
something you have to go do.

00:38:02.060 --> 00:38:07.214
But to recreate that, I think
you need to do something else.

00:38:07.214 --> 00:38:08.880
And I don't know what
the answer to that

00:38:08.880 --> 00:38:11.670
