00:38:58.320 --> 00:39:00.020
And that wasn't a
manufactured thing.

00:39:00.020 --> 00:39:06.010
That became a hit several
years after it was released.

00:39:06.010 --> 00:39:09.900
There have always
been low budget horror

00:39:09.900 --> 00:39:12.770
films and low budget B movies.

00:39:15.740 --> 00:39:17.920
And actually, they're
kind of dying out,

00:39:17.920 --> 00:39:20.580
