00:39:54.790 --> 00:39:57.440
right now as to how
smaller projects are

00:39:57.440 --> 00:40:00.780
going to find an audience.

00:40:00.780 --> 00:40:05.840
So I don't know that we
invented anything new,

00:40:05.840 --> 00:40:10.590
