00:40:18.385 --> 00:40:20.940
Never mind.

00:40:20.940 --> 00:40:21.440
Yeah.

00:40:24.470 --> 00:40:25.130
I don't know.

00:40:25.130 --> 00:40:31.240
I think the more they try
